... Rc1+ {[%emt 0:07:27]} 27. Kh2 {[%emt 0:00:16]} (27. Nf1 Nb2 $17 {[%csl Rd2,Rd6][%cal Gb7d5,Gd5c4,Gb2c4]}) 27... Rh1+ {[%emt 0:03:36]} 28. Kg3 {[%emt 0:00:08]} Ne5 {[%emt 0:00:16]} (28... Ne1 29. Ne4) 29. Rd4 {[%emt 0:01:54]} (29. Rf4+ Kg8 30. Nhf3 Nf7 $17 {[%csl Rd6][%cal Yd6f5]}) 29... Rg5+ {[%emt 0:03:11]} 30. Kf4 {[%emt 0:00:52]} Kf6 {[%emt 0:00:03]} 31. g4 {[%emt 0:03:50][%cal Gf4g3]} (31. Ne4+ Bxe4 32. Rexe4 Nc4 33. Rd3 Re5 34. Rf3 g5+ 35. Kg4+ Kg7 36. Rxe5 Nxe5+ 37. Kxg5 Nxf3+ 38. Nxf3 Rd1 $19) 31... Rxg4+ {[%emt 0:00:23]} 32. hxg4 {[%emt 0:00:07]} g5+ {[%emt 0:00:04]} 33. Kg3 {[%emt 0:00:12]} gxh4+ {[%emt 0:00:44]} 34. Kf4 {[%emt 0:00:12]} Ng6# {[%emt 0:00:00]} 0-1

